---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout	title="About Me - Jitan Gupta" description="Jitan Gupta is a full-stack engineer turned an entrepreneur.">
	<section class="bg-gray-100">
		<div class="bg-white max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 rounded-b-2xl">
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:space-x-8">
				<img src="/jitan-bg.png" alt="Jitan Gupta" class="h-[450px] md:h-[350px]">
				<div class="mt-6 mb-6 md:mt-0">
					<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Hey, I’m <span class="theme-t-green">Jitan Gupta</span> 👋</h1>
					<p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
						I still remember the first time I deployed an app—excited, nervous, and praying it wouldn’t crash. A decade later, I’ve built enterprise-grade systems from scratch, tackled debugging nightmares, and migrated legacy software into scalable cloud solutions.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
						I’m a <span class="font-semibold">full-stack engineer</span> involved in every phase of software development. But beyond the code, my real passion is <span class="font-semibold">teaching and mentoring</span>.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
						I love helping students, early-career developers, and IT professionals transitioning into tech. That’s why I write articles and break down complex topics into bite-sized, practical lessons that you can apply right away.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 mb-6">
						Now, I’m launching a <span class="font-semibold">YouTube channel</span> where I share real-world coding challenges, architecture insights, and career hacks—everything I wish I had when I started.
					</p>					
					<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@jitangupta" class="bg-orange-300 text-gray-900 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-orange-400 transition">Subscribe on YouTube</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="w-full h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent my-8"></div>
			<!-- Expertise Section -->
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">💡 Here is what you can expect:</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
				  <li class="flex items-center gap-2">⚙️ Full-stack development with .NET, EF Core, Angular, and Azure</li>
				  <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🛠️ Designing scalable cloud solutions</li>
				  <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🚀 Debugging & migrating legacy software</li>
				  <li class="flex items-center gap-2">📈 Navigating career growth in tech</li>
				</ul>
			  </div>
			
			  <!-- Closing Statement -->
			  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-6 text-lg text-gray-700 text-center">
				<p>
				  I believe software development isn’t just about writing code—it’s about problem-solving, designing scalable systems, and continuously learning. If that’s what you’re here for, let’s build something great together!
				</p>
			  </div>
		</div>
		
	</section>
</Layout>
